# Region host and workflow GUID are intentionally committed in the OpenAPI files (user-approved).
# The only true secret is the SAS signature (sig), which is never stored in any file
# (it is entered at plugin install time). The rules below are generic hygiene to avoid
# accidentally committing local overrides or secrets.
*.local.yaml
*.local.yml
*.local.json

# Files that might accidentally hold the SAS signature (sig) or other secrets
*.secret
*.secret.*
.env
.env.*
